    SelectExpression
    Corresponds to a queries like "select 2*x, x+sum(y+3) from t[...] where x>5 group by x" chain of data/processing (D=Data, P=Processing, agg=aggregate): (D1) inputDef (x,y) (P1.1) where filter (x>5) (P1.2) aggInputList (D2) aggInputDef (x,y+3) (P2) aggSelectList (D3) aggOutputDef (x,sum(y+3)) (P3) selectList (D4) outputDef (2*x,x+sum(y+3)) P1.2 is performed by the WindowProcessor If there is no aggregate, then P3 follows directly after P1.1
